      "writtenOn": "2021-05-07T21:32:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "well, theoretically it is derivable even with the data we have today if the assumption that CV will submit CLs one by one in submission order. Therefore, the first cl in the `Cls` this is missing in `SubmittedCls` is failure and the rest would be pending. \n\nI can certainly make it explicit in run.Submission because I\u0027m planning to add the failed CL information in the completion event submitter send to RM to provide customized user communication (i.e. CV will post error message only to failed CL and post \"dependent CL not submitted\" to the pending CLs).\n\nMaybe before that, we can implement the workaround I\u0027ve mentioned above or simply add a TODO.",
